description: Regularisation of zero flow

description: = true, if opening is filtered with a 2nd order CriticalDamping filter

name: checkvalve_1.leakageOpening

name: chiller_1._dp_start
description: Start value for dp, used to avoid a warning if not set in dp, and to avoid dp.start in parameter window

name: chiller_1._m_flow_start
description: Start value for m_flow, used to avoid a warning if not set in m_flow, and to avoid m_flow.start in parameter window

name: chiller_1.allowFlowReversal
description: = false to simplify equations, assuming, but not enforcing, no flow reversal

name: chiller_1.coeff
description: Precomputed coefficient to avoid division by parameter

name: chiller_1.computeFlowResistance
description: Flag to enable/disable computation of flow resistance

name: chiller_1.deltaM
description: Fraction of nominal mass flow rate where transition to turbulent occurs

name: chiller_1.dp
description: Pressure difference between port_a and port_b

name: chiller_1.dp_nominal
description: Pressure drop at nominal mass flow rate

name: chiller_1.dp_nominal_pos
description: Absolute value of nominal pressure difference

name: chiller_1.eta_default
description: Dynamic viscosity, used to compute transition to turbulent flow regime

name: chiller_1.from_dp
description: = true, use m_flow = f(dp) else dp = f(m_flow)

name: chiller_1.homotopyInitialization
description: = true, use homotopy method

name: chiller_1.k
description: Flow coefficient, k=m_flow/sqrt(dp), with unit=(kg.m)^(1/2)

name: chiller_1.linearized
description: = true, use linear relation between m_flow and dp for any flow rate

name: chiller_1.m_flow
description: Mass flow rate from port_a to port_b (m_flow > 0 is design flow direction)

name: chiller_1.m_flow_nominal
description: Nominal mass flow rate

name: chiller_1.m_flow_nominal_pos
description: Absolute value of nominal flow rate

name: chiller_1.m_flow_small
description: Small mass flow rate for regularization of zero flow

name: chiller_1.m_flow_turbulent
description: Turbulent flow if |m_flow| >= m_flow_turbulent

name: chiller_1.port_a.h_outflow
description: Specific thermodynamic enthalpy close to the connection point if m_flow < 0

name: chiller_1.port_a.m_flow
description: Mass flow rate from the connection point into the component

name: chiller_1.port_a.p
description: Thermodynamic pressure in the connection point

name: chiller_1.port_b.h_outflow
description: Specific thermodynamic enthalpy close to the connection point if m_flow < 0

name: chiller_1.port_b.m_flow
description: Mass flow rate from the connection point into the component

name: chiller_1.port_b.p
description: Thermodynamic pressure in the connection point

name: chiller_1.show_T
description: = true, if actual temperature at port is computed

name: chiller_1.sta_default.T
description: Temperature of medium

name: chiller_1.sta_default.p
description: Absolute pressure of medium
